Thanks for the feedback! If your issue is related to the Flutter framework itself,
please open an issue at
[github.com/flutter/flutter](https://github.com/flutter/flutter/issues/new).

## What happened

Launched Android Studio into project selection window, that is, without re-opening the last project.

## Version information

Android Studio `4.1 Beta 1` • Flutter plugin `io.flutter 46.0.3` • Dart plugin `201.7223.99`

Error getting Flutter sdk information.

null

comment_data.body: The beta and canary version of Android Studio need to get the plugin via the dev channel.

title: PluginException when launching Android Studio (project selection)
